Rating: 4
I have made this several times and it is universally appreciated. You must not substitute another type of steak, as you must have a very tender cut. I have always used ciabatta bread for the sandwiches with great results. IME, it is important NOT to brush oil on the steaks. The time I did, I had major flare-ups and charrred meat. The potatoes are quite delicious as well.

