Rating: 3
Very good. Its also very simple to make. The chimichurri sauce is what makes this dish. I made a couple of small changes. I had fresh thyme & garlic chives so i added a little bit of both to the sauce. When i was grilling the steak i also grilled thick sliced onions and put them on top of the sandwich. I used some thin cut tbone steaks that were perfect for this recipe and cut the meat off the bone after grilling. Some changes i might make in the future would be to add a chipotle and maybe a little cumin to the sauce. Hey its not traditional but either is cilantro. Just cause its not traditional though does not mean its not good.

